Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ed Meese investigation
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcw5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Apr 1984
Special prosecutor appointed to look into financial background of Ed Meese, the president's choice as next attorney general. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less